<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.4">
<l>uṟiyai muṟṟat turuṭṭiniṉ ṟāṭuvār</l>
<l>naṟuney pāltayir naṉṟākat tūvuvār</l>
<l>ceṟimeṉ kūnta laviḻat tiḷaittuveṅku</l>
<l>maṟiva ḻintaṉa rāyppāṭi yāyarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They dance continuously, whirling about the rope-shelf in the courtyard;</l>
<l>they happily sprinkle fragrant ghee, milk, and curds;</l>
<l>everywhere swinging to and fro such that [their] thick, soft tresses became loose,</l>
<l>the cowherds of the cowherd village have lost their minds!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
